<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">年度轿跑型SUV：</span></strong></span><span>一汽-大众奥迪Q3轿跑</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>年度智能SUV：</strong></span><span>上汽荣威RX5 MAX</span></p>
